- **Add M2 feature**: Update T6 progress in ROADMAP.md, ensure REQUIREMENTS reflects memory system
- **Fix blocker**: Document in ROADMAP.md Blockers section, flag for discussion
- **Add new game mechanic**: Update src/game.js state shape, update REQUIREMENTS.md if scope-changing
- **Optimize tokens**: Review memory retrieval scoring in src/game.js, compact summaries in src/ai.js
- **Improve AI responses**: Adjust JSON schema in src/ai.js or system prompts
- **Enhance UI**: Modify public/app.js and public/styles.css, test mobile
- **Debug state issues**: Check SQLite queries in src/db.js and state mutations in src/game.js

